<Layout title="CMJ - Outreach Page">
  <h1>Get Involved in Closing the Wage Gap!</h1>
  
  <p>Want to learn more about the issue of the wage gap or get involved in the fight for wage equality? Look no further!</p>
  <p>Here are some places where you can find more info and take action to make a real impact:</p>

  <h2>Further Information on the Issue:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.epi.org/publication/closing-the-pay-gap-and-beyond/" target="_blank">Closing the Pay Gap and Beyond - Economic Policy Institute</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.tuc.org.uk/research-analysis/reports/double-trouble-ethnicity-gender-pay-gap" target="_blank">Double Trouble: The Ethnicity Gender Pay Gap</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Ways to Get Involved:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.equalpaytoday.org/" target="_blank">Join the Equal Pay Today Campaign</a> — A campaign by Equal Rights Advocates focusing on gender and racial wage gap</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.equalpayinternationalcoalition.org/" target="_blank">Join the Equal Pay International Coalition (EPIC)</a> — A coalition led by ILO, UN Women, and OECD focusing on the gender wage gap</li>
    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/ethnicity-pay-gap-campaign-dianne-greyson/" target="_blank">Support the Ethnicity Pay Gap Campaign</a> — A campaign led by Dianne Greyson focused on the racial wage gap</li>
  </ul>

</Layout>

